claim.claim-text:
1. A method for producing par-baked pizza crusts, comprising: 
mixing a plurality of ingredients to produce pizza crust dough; 
forming the dough into a sheet; 
cutting a plurality of dough portions out of the sheet; 
depositing the dough portions on a pan; 
proofing the dough portions; 
positioning a lid assembly to contact the proofed dough portions; and 
par-baking the dough portions in an oven while the lid assembly is in contact with the dough portions to produce par-baked pizza crusts.
